name: Princess Leia (V)
Lore: 'Prominent leader in the struggling Alliance. Former member of the Imperial Senate. Beginning to discover her true heritage. Likes scoundrels.',
Text: 'May deploy or move as a ''react'' to same site as an Imperial. Adds one battle destiny if with Han or Vader. During your deploy phase, may deploy one Leia Of Alderaan, Reflection, or a matching blaster on Leia from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 4.',
